follow right with these. First of all, how do you 
explain your tremendous flurry of expansion in

10:35.543 --> 10:40.611
the 1960s for the lab here. Was it ONR and outside 
source funds or what? Well, it was primarily

10:44.777 --> 11:03.306
because Bookhouse saw a number of the things that 
