13:18.573 --> 13:31.590
return to the university, much less head the major 
establishment of marine biology at the

13:18.573 --> 13:31.590
university. How do you explain that? Well, I 
thought about it, and you know, I never will really

13:34.374 --> 13:39.260
know. The fight over inbreeding occurred 
