14:20.118 --> 14:24.104
decided to do it anyway. So that by the time the 67 
appointment came around, that issue had already

14:25.145 --> 14:30.794
been decided. And I assume that the university, in 
looking at potential candidates for the job, saw

14:32.496 --> 14:43.373
in me a person who was already settled in Beaufort 
and therefore apparently compatible with a small

14:44.483 --> 14:47.207
town. I had been the mayor of the town for two terms. 
