14:50.633 --> 14:57.303
endeavors like school bond referendum and that 
sort of thing. My academic record, other than

14:57.323 --> 15:07.960
teaching, for which I was not employed, was 
acceptable in terms of publication, involvement

14:57.323 --> 15:07.960
with national and international things. My 
administrative capacity had only been viewed

15:09.745 --> 15:19.477
through the management of research grants, of 
which I had at one time four or five. And I assumed

15:20.558 --> 15:29.669
that putting all those things together, they 
decided that rather than betting on a new horse,

15:20.558 --> 15:29.669
they would take a chance and bet on one that they 
knew. But

15:29.689 --> 15:35.736
that's all speculation, because nobody's ever 
told me.

