primarily 1947 ideas. And the direction that you

18:52.613 --> 18:57.059
get out of that sort of information is downhill. So 
that I will only continue to serve as director of

18:58.280 --> 19:06.931
this laboratory as long as provisions are made for 
me to have some time for research. And if that day

19:07.532 --> 19:15.702
does not, if the day comes when that is not 
possible, then somebody else can be director.

