20:43.988 --> 20:49.457
out to other institutions, so the whole thing 
builds up to a feedback mechanism. And that's

20:49.477 --> 20:50.678
where we are now. The gentleman teaching the 
marine invertebrate zoology course this summer

20:51.400 --> 21:01.616
at Beaufort is Robert Barnes, author of most 
