sure that one of the reasons Bob came back is that he 
enjoys teaching here. Some number of students

21:18.953 --> 21:22.637
came to that course this summer because he's 
teaching here. And they will provide further

21:23.598 --> 21:28.343
feedback in 1983, 4, 5, and 6. We have expanded that 
traditional role to the international realm. And

21:33.950 --> 21:40.817
we're now in the third year of our so-called 
international training program, which I

21:33.950 --> 21:40.817
mentioned earlier. That will, in time, provide us 
with feedback from all over the world. And I think

21:46.929 --> 21:55.843
this is a very vital role that this laboratory can 
play as a facility of a privately endowed

21:46.929 --> 21:55.843
university. We are totally apart from any real 
political influence. And I think we have a

22:03.615 --> 22:06.340
responsibility that goes with that. Then you see 
