departments. So we have people here who are 
affiliated with departments in biochemistry,

25:43.531 --> 25:54.542
geology, botany, zoology, chemistry, and 
physiology med school. So that here is a very broad

25:56.125 --> 26:07.759
base from which to develop research programs, 
training programs, student involvement at

25:56.125 --> 26:07.759
either the state, national, or international 
level. And we've already begun to develop that.

