the third setos hair on the fourth abdominal

26:24.273 --> 26:35.808
appendage, then that's what they become known 
for. Well, that's not our interest at all. We want

26:39.973 --> 26:50.466
to have a broad base which will provide the proper 
research facilities, experience, and training

26:39.973 --> 26:50.466
for people who will go out and send their students 
back here. And I think that you see your role in

26:52.555 --> 27:00.864
